               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of al-Risālah al-Ghawthīyah</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh85089353 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2008112367" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1066-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>The Arabic text of <title key="work_5250">al-Risālah
                              al-Ghawthīyah</title> by <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164659026.0x000001 viaf_95223177" role="aut">Ibn al-ʻArabī, 1165-1240</persName> with an anonymous prose
                           translation and commentary in Persian.
                        </p>
                        <p>Accompanied (ff.2v-57r) in the margins by an anonymous verse translation
                           in Persian.</p>
                        <p>61ff, lacuna after f. 57; 14 lines per page; fair taʻliq with Arabic text
                           in naskhi; interlinear Persian in red ink; copyist? Shāh-i Miskīn; dated
                           at Hamgadah (India) 2 Jum. I 1120 (20 July 1708).</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22912">Sharḥ-i Ghaws̱īyah</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_22912">شرح غوثیہ</title>
